
// This Hyperlambda code sets the value of the [.post_body] node to the value retrieved from the [body] node within the [content] node, which is a child of the [http.get] node. The [set-value] slot is used to assign the value, while the [get-value] slot retrieves the specified value from the node structure.
set-value:x:@.post_body
   get-value:x:@http.get/*/content/*/body
